 article changed the way I will take responsiblity for the cards I play and respect those my opponents play. Impressive, Most impressive. Question what about stacking while using a search mechanic...is that really cheating? </FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD>&nbsp;</TD><TD><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><A HREF="/swccg/membercenter/directory/memberpage.php3?member=158">C'boath</A></FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD VALIGN="TOP" ALIGN="RIGHT" WIDTH="10%"><IMG SRC="images/a5.gif" BORDER=0></TD><TD VALIGN="TOP" WIDTH="90%"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">so true. i agree 100%. i espically agree with the your cards are your responibility part.<br>
