<br>
At level one, if I &quot;forget&quot; I&#146;m told to remember.  If I &quot;forget&quot; again, I get a caution.  If I get a second caution I get a warning.  If I get a second warning I get a game loss.<br>
<br>
At level two, I don&#146;t get a caution, then a warning, then a game loss.<br>
<br>
At level three I get a warning, then a game loss.<br>
<br>
At level four (ProTour - World Championship) I get a warning and a game loss.<br>
<br>
Star Wars tournaments have tolerated cheating way too much.  Cut the disease out.<br>
<br>
Kirk<br>
Kirk@unias.net<br>
